    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, keeping her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and only bringing her out for sunny weekend cruises. She drives like she just rolled off the assembly line\u2014smooth, responsive, and purely joyful. You might spot a microscopic speck on the bumper if you really go looking, but honestly, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. I\u2019m looking for a good home for her where she\u2019ll get the love she deserves!",
      "price": 46500.0,
