    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade specimen, meticulously sorted for the discerning driver who demands surgical precision. The powertrain features a fully refreshed top-end with reinforced VANOS units and a bespoke ECU map optimized for linear power delivery across the entire rev range. We have proactively addressed the chassis' structural integrity with a comprehensive subframe reinforcement kit, ensuring zero flex under high-load cornering. The footwork is managed by corner-balanced coilovers with 30-way adjustable dampening, significantly reducing unsprung mass for telepathic turn-in. Every fluid has been cycled with high-temp synthetics, and the limited-slip differential locks up with factory-spec tightness. This is a bulletproof, mechanically perfected machine that feels more planted and responsive than the day it left the showroom floor. No deferred maintenance, no compromises\u2014just pure, analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
