    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a living dream with this breathtaking automotive masterpiece. More than just a vehicle, this is a time capsule that captures the very essence of open-road romance. Its silhouette cuts through the air with the grace of a predator, while the deep, lustrous finish shimmers like a still lake at dawn. Inside, you are enveloped in a sanctuary of pristine, butter-soft leather that still carries the rich aroma of old-world craftsmanship. To drive it is to conduct a mechanical symphony, where every purr of the engine and every seamless shift tells a story of prestige and untamed soul. This is your invitation to own not just a car, but a legacy preserved in perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
