    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute benchmark in automotive excellence. This vehicle arrives in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, having undergone a rigorous multi-point certification process to ensure mechanical and aesthetic perfection. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, while the interior remains in pristine, untouched form. For the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than the finest, this specimen represents a rare find that combines investment-grade quality with peerless performance. Experience the confidence of driving a vehicle that looks, feels, and performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 48900.0,
