    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. You know, it\u2019s not every day you come across a beauty like this one. I\u2019ve spent more weekends than I can count polishing her up and just admiring those lines\u2014she\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, walking into the garage and seeing that shine is the highlight of my day! She\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking just like she did on the showroom floor. Every little detail has been pampered, and while she\u2019s enjoyed a few sunny drives, she\u2019s been treated with nothing but love and covered storage. This isn\u2019t just a car; it\u2019s a member of the family looking for a new home where she'll be appreciated. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so head-over-heels for this ride!",
      "price": 46500.0,
